{"tid":1965680,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌你老母 個保就業計劃根本變相利益輸送","createTime":"2020-04-09T15:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T15:35:09.000Z","uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3408a2257927a33bdb517d272ba1fea10cef8a98","tid":1965680,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"如何預防僱主取得津貼後，不解僱員工？<br />\n<br />\n羅：原則是第一，僱主取得津貼後，要用於僱員上。第二，裁員是不能發生的，但是否代表不能「炒人」？假設有僱員因犯錯或自己要離職，則無法阻止，所以是指不能「減size」，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即不能減少僱員人數</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 即係隨便炒人<br />\n如果我係酒樓食肆老細 我炒撚晒所有員工<br />\n然後請晒自己親朋戚友 咁樣白賺幾十萬<br />\n咪話唔和味<br />\n打工仔結果咪又係失業 <br />\n有無人駁到我?"},{"pid":"63ce9f77b5868e90a510fccef07d59b2207a6c26","tid":1965680,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"我有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0abfb56c012d8ab169d15e23a39c0ad28132e6","tid":1965680,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}